{"tid":1061613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★靚女OL巴士晾腳好自在　網民睇見眼凸","createTime":"2019-03-14T13:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T15:25:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":184,"uniUserReply":124,"replies":[{"pid":"7cf4c3cd8603df197a4d29ed87af5db42004e15c","tid":1061613,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T13:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190314/photo/bkn-20190314171433157-0314_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190314181441\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190314%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190314171433157-0314_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190314181441&h=44d21f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭車要顧己及人，但總有自私者圖舒適，罔顧他人。今日（14日）一名年輕女子在巴士車廂上不但雙腿「飛象過河」至對面座位，更以手袋霸佔鄰座。一人霸3座位行徑，被網民怒斥，「後生細女，知唔知禮貌？」<br />\n<br />\n有網民於 Facebook 群組「香港特發事故報料區」發文指，今日早上9時許，乘坐巴士時，目擊一名年輕女子在車廂下層公然「飛象過河」，且雙腳沒有脫鞋，連鞋帶腳晾在對面座椅。而女子的名牌手袋則放在左邊座位，一人霸3座位令網民嘩然。<br />\n<br />\n有網民斥責女子年輕卻沒禮貌，「老人家唔識仲可以理解，咁後生都咁做係發生咩事？」有網民猜測女子為年輕上班族，斥「打扮咁得體，坐成咁？好唔好意思啊？」「晨早流流嘅車，斷估唔會係放工好攰啩？」有網民認為香港年輕人都非常注意形象，估計女子是旅客，「香港人點會咁做，一定係遊客。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190314/bkn-20190314171433157-0314_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190314%2Fbkn-20190314171433157-0314_00822_001.html&d=%2FIrJ3RR%2Fwz8SFLZOEAJhptjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=27a6f38e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190314/bkn-20190314171433157-0314_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ac56cff892f5cd7e1a7706aa9dfd5cb1236cd52a","tid":1061613,"uid":19454,"like":85,"dislike":7,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T13:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193355d7ee4dbd2a5d8557d06b7252d5c6d869